C++ Programming Practice
*****************************************************************************************************
###General Programs
hello.cpp 	: Simple Hello World program
prog1.cpp 	: A program to print number in various formats (decimal, octal, hex etc.)
prog2.cpp 	: A program to accept decimal number and print in decimal, octal and hex format
prog3.cpp 	: A program to demonstrate the string class
prog4.cpp 	: A program to read and write files. Copying README file to sample.txt
prog5.cpp 	: A program to read sample.txt and store it in a string object and print it completely
prog6.cpp 	: A simple program to demonstrate vector. Reading sample.txt into a vector and printing it
prog7.cpp 	: A simple program to demonstrate vector. Reading sample.txt into a vector and printing it
*****************************************************************************************************
C in C++
prog8.cpp 	: A simple program to print size of various data types, specifiers and pointers (both 32 bit and 64 bit)
prog9.cpp 	: A simple program to print address of variable and function
prog10.cpp 	: A program to demonstrate pass by value and pass by reference
prog11.cpp	: A simple program to demonstrate void pointer and type casting
